data.text:
Well, now's as good a time as any to post the first version of the 09/10 season's YA catchall thread.

Thanks as always to those of you who have helped in various ways by posting news, tracking transfers, following Mexican registrations, etc.

This is a work in constant progress and I anticipate quite a few additions and changes between now and the end of the month (and beyond). I'm working on a very long list of players whose whereabouts I still need to confirm.

Please keep the comments, questions, corrections, updates, etc., coming.
